long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Need to edit query string parameters but having a rough time navigating around chrome's single-line URL bar? Have no fear! urled is here to save the day. When you click on the "UE" button, you'll be able to load the URL into a multiline texteditor preformatted to make the URL easier to edit. When you click 'Finish', the url will replace your current url.
